SubjectRegulations Amending the Regulations Implementing the United Nations Resolutions on the Democratic Peopleâ€™s Republic of Korea (DPRK)
PrecisRegulations amending the REGULATIONS IMPLEMENTING THE UNITED NATIONS RESOLUTIONS ON THE DEMOCRATIC PEOPLE'S REPUBLIC OF KOREA (DPRK) in order to (1) implement Resolutions 2321 (2016) and 2397 (2017) in full and fulfill Canada's international legal obligation to implement the binding decisions of the Security Council; and (2) address miscellaneous amendments raised by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
